description.en:
Highlander Network bringing Proof-of-Stake "ONEX" Token to Ethereum Classic platform.

While keeping tokens holders protection in mind, ONEX utilizes ERC223 token standard. ONEX is the first to implement the Proof-of-Stake mechanism on Ethereum Classic, meaning that holders of ONEX can earn some extra tokens just by holding ONEX for a period of time, greater than or equal to The Minimum Coin Age.
